-- Comments for future AI plan generation
-- ============================================================================
-- When generating personalized plans:
-- 1. Create entry in user_study_plans with ai_generated=true
-- 2. Generate daily tasks for each day in the plan's date range
-- 3. Link tasks to plan via plan_id
-- 4. Set generated_by='ai_personalized'
-- 5. Use AI to determine optimal task sequence, difficulty progression
-- 6. Consider user's:
--    - Current level (from mastery data)
--    - Weak areas (from performance)
--    - Time until exam (urgency)
--    - Study habits (from activity data)
